title: Oberwölz Stadt
text: Oberwölz Stadt is a town and a former municipality in the district of <a href="Murau%20%28district%29">Murau</a> in the <a href="Austria">Austria</a>n state of <a href="Styria">Styria</a>. Since the 2015 <a href="Styria%20municipal%20structural%20reform">Styria municipal structural reform</a>, it is part of the municipality <a href="Oberw%C3%B6lz">Oberwölz</a>.
